Project AWARE is a member of the Global Ghost Gear Initiative https://www.ghostgear.org/, Seas At Risk http://www.seas-at-risk.org,  International Non Governmental Member of IUCN http://iucn.org/about/union/members/who_members/members_database/, and a Founding member of the Trash Free Seas Alliance http://www.oceanconservancy.org/our-work/our-partners/trash-free-seas-alliance.html &#xd;
&#xd;
We are not a membership organization, however, we do have supporters and volunteers in virtually all EU member states.
